 n n                  U Eyebrow menu UIC Connection Student Affairs UIC menu UIC edu Campus Map  n nUIC Logo n n n n UIC Logo  n          ID Center n         ID Center Our Mission nThe mission of the ID Center is to support the university community with a standardized and convenient form of identification  The ID Center strives to equip the card as a means to provide access to related university systems and services  A dedicated staff is committed to serving all customers in an efficient and courteous manner  The ID Center will endeavor to bring expanded uses of the card through advances in technology and innovation What we do nThe ID Center provides a one  We directly support the production of i Our satellite ID Center on the west campus supports the medical   professional community with ID creation services close to their offices and classrooms Contact Information for Main ID Center  n n n n n n            CTA U PASS n         n n                Your U Pass provides you unlimited rides on the CTA during your enrollment as a full time student at the University  n             n n  n n n n n n            Identification Cards n         n n                Your i card is your official permanent ID card and will be used as long as you attend or are employed by the University  n             n n  n n n n n n            Dragon Dollar  n         n n                The Dragon Dollar  program is the official campus debit account linked to your i card  n             n n Locations  n nUIC Logo n n n n UIC Logo  n          ID Center n         Contact idcenter uic edu Social Media Accounts  nFacebook n Facebook  nTwitter n Twitter  nInstagram n Instagram  nYouTube n YouTube UIC edu links UIC edu Academic Calendar Athletics Campus Directory Disability Resources Emergency Information Event Calendar Job Openings Library Maps UIC Today UI Health Veterans Affairs Privacy Statement Campuses University of Illinois System Urbana Champaign Springfield Cookie Settings 